description: In this video, I show you how to make vegan cornbread. This easy vegan cornbread recipe only requires one bowl to make! It was the most popular recipe on my blog in 2017 and considering I post a LOT of recipes, that's pretty impressive stuff! Now you can have homemade cornbread in less than 30 minutes. Perfect served along with chili or just alone as a snack, this is my all-time favourite cornbread recipe!
name: Easy Vegan Cornbread - How to Make Vegan Cornbread
